---
const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<section
    id="top"
    class="relative h-screen min-h-[600px] flex flex-col justify-center items-center bg-white text-black overflow-hidden border-b border-black selection:bg-black selection:text-white"
>
    <div
        class="absolute inset-0 z-0 h-full w-full bg-[radial-gradient(#e5e7eb_1px,transparent_1px)] [background-size:24px_24px]"
    >
    </div>


    <div class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center text-center px-4">
        <p
            class="font-mono text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6 uppercase tracking-[0.2em] animate-fade-in-down"
        >
            Desarrollo de software freelance
        </p>

        <h1
            class="font-black text-[13vw] md:text-[14vw] leading-[0.8] tracking-tighter uppercase flex flex-col select-none"
        >
            <span class="block text-black"> Djillali </span>
            <span
                class="block text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-b from-gray-700 via-gray-500 to-gray-400"
            >
                Adair
            </span>
        </h1>

        <p class="mt-6 max-w-xl text-gray-600 font-medium text-sm md:text-base">
            Soy <strong class="text-black">Djillali Adair</strong>, también
            conocido como <strong class="text-black">@AngoZero</strong>.
            Diseño y construyo soluciones digitales adaptadas a tu operación, tu idea o tu proyecto.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-center gap-6">
            <div
                class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-stretch sm:items-center gap-4 w-full sm:w-auto px-4 sm:px-0"
            >
                <a
                    href="#contact"
                    class="px-6 py-3 border-2 border-black font-mono uppercase tracking-widest text-xs hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors text-center"
                >
                    Solicitar propuesta
                </a>
            </div>

            <a
                href="https://github.com/AngoZero"
                target="_blank"
                rel="noopener noreferrer"
                class="group cursor-pointer"
                aria-label="Perfil de GitHub de AngoZero"
            >
                <div
                    class="h-[1px] w-0 group-hover:w-full bg-black transition-all duration-300"
                >
                </div>
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>

</section>
